    %% в”Ђв”Ђ Backend internal в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ

    Rel(py_ws, sio, "Room: forward trackingEvent\nв†’ Socket.io emit detection, personDetected, motionDetected", "EventEmitter")
    Rel(sio, stream_mgr, "requestStream / stopStream\nviewer socket ID tracking", "Socket.io events")
    Rel(stream_ctrl, stream_mgr, "Read .lastFrame for JPEG snapshot\nRead viewer counts for metrics", "Direct access")
